ght-attackers-trump-inspired-cesar-sayoc-wasnt-the-first-and-wont-be-the-last/" data-reactid="258"><div class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-thumbnail" data-reactid="259"><img height="440" src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/f874bb14-b214-453a-a902-7b0c4d71665e/f874bb14-b214-453a-a902-7b0c4d71665e.bin?auto=compress,format&amp;cs=srgb&amp;dpr=2&amp;h=440&amp;w=440&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces%2Cedges&amp;_=8e429da38bcd5b556619bf84b81109f0" width="440" data-reactid="260"/></div><h4 class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-title" data-reactid="261">Here Is a List of Far-Right Attackers Trump Inspired. Cesar Sayoc Wasn’t the First — and Won’t Be the Last.</h4></a></div><div class="RelatedPosts-promo" data-reactid="262"><a href="https://theintercept.com/2019/02/23/france-islamophobia-islam-french-muslims-terrorism/" data-reactid="263"><div class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-thumbnail" data-reactid="264"><img height="440" src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/a9d2f910-b05c-4905-94f0-9c2f2ffdd778/a9d2f910-b05c-4905-94f0-9c2f2ffdd778.bin?auto=compress,format&amp;cs=srgb&amp;dpr=2&amp;h=440&amp;w=440&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces%2Cedges&amp;_=7740bf08124052570a272bccb688ae05" width="440" data-reactid="265"/></div><h4 class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-title" data-reactid="266">French Muslims Grapple With a Republic That Codified Their Marginalization</h4></a></div><div class="RelatedPosts-promo" data-reactid="267"><a href="https://theintercept.com/2018/12/25/strange-death-of-europe-douglas-murray-review/" data-reactid="268"><div class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-thumbnail" data-reactid="269"><img height="440" src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/2d795d8f-0478-46c8-be4b-fbab28ff3128/2d795d8f-0478-46c8-be4b-fbab28ff3128.bin?auto=compress,format&amp;cs=srgb&amp;dpr=2&amp;h=440&amp;w=440&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces%2Cedges&amp;_=a7926f00555deefc18dcbc4f5bb2b762" width="440" data-reactid="270"/></div><h4 class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-title" data-reactid="271">The Far Right Is Obsessed With a Book About Muslims Destroying Europe. Here’s What It Gets Wrong.</h4></a></div></div><div class="Post-latest-articles" data-reactid="272"><h4 class="Post-latest-articles-header" data-reactid="273">Latest Stories</h4><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="274"><div data-reactid="275"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="276"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/18/trump-latin-america-foreign-policy-joe-biden/" data-reactid="277"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="278"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="279"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="280"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="281"><noscript data-reactid="282"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/68115254-b698-4c8d-93e3-ae18f013e128/68115254-b698-4c8d-93e3-ae18f013e128.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=96d69908306e5168585e8e7a6f71fecb" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="283"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="284"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="285"><h4 class="Promo-title" data-reactid="286"><span class="Promo-title-wrap" data-reactid="287">We Need to Reverse the Damage Trump Has Done in Latin America. Biden’s Plans Don’t Cut It.</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="288"><!-- react-text: 289 -->John Washington<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="290"><!-- react-text: 291 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 292 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="293">Apr. 18</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="294"><!-- react-empty: 295 --></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="296"><div data-reactid="297"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="298"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/18/trump-urges-followers-risk-lives-rallies-wont-attend/" data-reactid="299"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="300"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="301"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="302"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="303"><noscript data-reactid="304"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/b2c9c56c-afe9-4ccc-8d4c-4397455ca432/b2c9c56c-afe9-4ccc-8d4c-4397455ca432.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=5da42725e1af7edf3c2cd744f22d72aa" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="305"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="306"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="307"><h4 class="Promo-title" data-reactid="308"><span class="Promo-title-wrap" data-reactid="309">If Trump Thinks It’s Safe for His Followers to Gather at Protests, Why Doesn’t He Attend One?</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="310"><!-- react-text: 311 -->Robert Mackey<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="312"><!-- react-text: 313 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 314 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="315">Apr. 18</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="316"><!-- react-empty: 317 --></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="318"><div data-reactid="319"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="320"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/17/coronavirus-fema-trump-misinformation/" data-reactid="321"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="322"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="323"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="324"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="325"><noscript da